    python ./code/13d_generate_cohort_analytics_figures.py --config ./configs/visium_cohort_clean.yaml --no-open

Recommended manuscript run:
    python ./code/13d_generate_cohort_analytics_figures.py --config ./configs/visium_cohort_clean.yaml --no-open --top-n-features 50

Figure set:
    01 PCA explained variance of retained spatial features
