    03 Program score distributions
    04 Cleaned label frequency
    04b Collapsed biological label-category frequency
    05 Glycolysis versus hypoxia-context scatter with regression/statistics
    06 Motif fraction matrix heatmap
    07 Motif fraction by motif
    08 Motif fragmentation by motif
    09 Mean centroid distance matrix between motifs
    10 Pairwise motif relationship counts
